  "3334930": {
    "name": "Galacticare - The Voice Beyond",
    "steam_appid": 3334930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/0ace05cb65e4d2a21878d767246a0fc6.webp?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生命、自由、公共健康。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此为银河文明的神圣支柱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，如今银河燃烧，战火蔓延，自由太空的存亡岌岌可危。诡谋再度归来——冷酷无情、潜伏无形，疯狂执着于抹杀宇宙间的一切生命。他们如瘟疫般横扫星际，所到之处尽是毁灭、阴谋以及灾难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/1f710d0e0bdd00c3cfac1eae1fb85854.poster.avif?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/1f710d0e0bdd00c3cfac1eae1fb85854.webm?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/1f710d0e0bdd00c3cfac1eae1fb85854.mp4?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/fe381d86e509392bd47c2e400341c9a6.webp?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为银河医疗保健的无畏领导者，你并非只是一名医院管理人员。在这场战争中，伤员与病患依赖你生存，而宇宙的命运也握在你的手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否在三个全新的全语音剧情战役关卡中智胜诡谋？修复战场上血肉模糊的士兵遗体，让他们重新投入战斗——在这风雨飘摇的银河之中，唯有你的独特医疗手段，才能扭转战局，拯救一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/5f448f6ab0bbe91f69ad4c05ec07d0b2.poster.avif?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/5f448f6ab0bbe91f69ad4c05ec07d0b2.webm?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/5f448f6ab0bbe91f69ad4c05ec07d0b2.mp4?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/dc3cd23468eba1207287cfa194801d99.webp?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们的低语能令盟友变成叛徒，令最先进的医疗机构沦为充满破坏与疾病的战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们已经潜入进来了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，院长，时间无多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/3a7e360dd0a1a13ea88a4675e5542c37.poster.avif?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/3a7e360dd0a1a13ea88a4675e5542c37.webm?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/3a7e360dd0a1a13ea88a4675e5542c37.mp4?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 被腐化的腾奇 - 那些可爱小猴子似的外星人，已变身为迷你终结者！破坏分子潜入医院，靠马桶炸弹和会爆炸的骨科诊疗间制造混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 全新外星病症 - 从“锐舞疹”、“感知错乱疹”到“激光伤”，这些新疾病狡猾至极，让你最优秀的顾问医师也束手无策。一次普通的诊断，可能在一杯咖啡的时间内，演变为星际级大流行病。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 无形之声 - 某个未知存在，在幕后操纵一切。他们的动机无人知晓，他们的触手无处不在。而最令人不解的是……为什么医院的洗手间又爆炸了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/35da54f26c949af36a4ae3de8fb3a64b.poster.avif?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/35da54f26c949af36a4ae3de8fb3a64b.webm?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/35da54f26c949af36a4ae3de8fb3a64b.mp4?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/ecdb2839282aa34ed5331afa81d178f6.webp?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜负不由等离子步枪或星舰决定（尽管它们确实派得上用场）。真正的胜利，将取决于绷带、医疗机器人，以及用医疗罐子和裂变材料临时拼凑的高爆炸药（保险不赔）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 抢救英雄 – 从灭绝的边缘挽救整个物种，修补他们支离破碎的身躯，再将他们送回惨烈的银河战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 智胜诡谋 – 部署安保科技，揪出破坏分子，在他们惹出大祸前阻止他们。毕竟，没人想让医院里充斥着无聊的寒暄，或者更糟——每个垃圾桶都被塞得满满当当。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 迎战不可思议的挑战 – 从救治遭受“激光伤”的西里战士，到击杀一尊远古宇宙神明，只有最强大的医院和最坚定的院长，才能熬过这一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/84e25c26d26b5a3d6525507bfd1f71ea.poster.avif?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/84e25c26d26b5a3d6525507bfd1f71ea.webm?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/84e25c26d26b5a3d6525507bfd1f71ea.mp4?t=1749639482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/cd748a76a6adf1395806b9db0b2816df.webp?t=1749639482\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >银河的未来在你手中，院长。你能否团结医护团队、救治伤员、击败诡谋？还是说，你的医疗帝国终将化作宇宙尘埃？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将决定所有智慧生命的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在……洗手消毒，穿戴整齐，准备迎接宇宙史上最混乱的医院值班吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334930/extras/224fc7e9e18db4065c65ad61a2a3adca.webp?t=1749639482\" width=600 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这就是《银河医疗保健：天外邪音》——恶搞科幻医院模拟游戏的爆炸性扩展篇。在这里，拯救生命只是开始。这场惊心动魄的全语音剧情冒险，势必让你战斗至最后一刻。</p>",
